    IParametricDropStrategy

  • Class Summary

    This strategy is a specialization in order to be able to drop Constraint inside constraint Property

    This strategy is a specialization in order to be able to drop Parameter inside Parameter Property this code is link to the parametric because the parameter as border item is only display in the parametric Diagram
